data.description:
JUST REDUCED! Charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers a generous layout with an open concept. This beautiful home combines style, comfort and functionality.   The kitchen features new appliances, updated countertops and plenty of counterspace.  Cozy up in the cold months with the wood burning fireplace. New tile floors have been installed along with a new garage door and new screen door. The master suite features a tub/shower combination, dual vanity and walk in closet. The remaining bedrooms are versatile, providing options for play rooms, guest rooms, or home office space. Located in the West Ridge Estates, this home is minutes from shopping, restaurants and medical facilities. The roof will be replaced at closing.  Schedule a showing today!
MEASUREMENTS ARE APPROXIMATE, BUYER TO VERIFY
